OL,3,CDoctors warns of exodus over pay
OL,5,FThe daily exodus of junior doctors out
OL,6,Fof Northern Ireland will continue
OL,7,Fwithout a "fair and just" pay deal,
OL,8,Fstriking medics have heard.
OL,10,FHundreds of doctors and supporters
OL,11,Fgathered outside Parliament Buildings
OL,12,Fat Stormont on Thursday on the first
OL,13,Fday of their latest 48-hour walkout
OL,14,Famid an ongoing industrial dispute
OL,15,Fover pay and retention issues.
OL,17,FThe strike began at 7am on Thursday
OL,18,Fand will end at the same time on
OL,19,FSaturday morning.
