OL,3,CDoctors warns of exodus over pay
OL,5,FIt comes after a similar 48-hour
OL,6,Fwalkout in May and a 24-hour strike in
OL,7,FMarch.
OL,9,FThe action in March was the first time
OL,10,Fjunior doctors had ever gone on strike
OL,11,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,13,FTheir union, BMA Northern Ireland, has
OL,14,Fcalled for a commitment to full pay
OL,15,Frestoration to 2008 levels, claiming
OL,16,Fthat junior doctors have seen their
OL,17,Fsalaries effectively eroded by 30%
OL,18,Fover the last 15 years due to a
OL,19,Ffailure to make pay awards in line
OL,20,Fwith inflation.
