OL,3,CDoctors warns of exodus over pay
OL,5,FThe BMA says newly qualified medics in
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland see colleagues
OL,7,Fworking elsewhere in the UK and in
OL,8,Fother jurisdictions getting better pay
OL,9,Fand conditions for less pressurised
OL,10,Fworkloads, and warned doctors are
OL,11,Fleaving the health service in
OL,12,Fincreasing numbers.
OL,14,FDoctors marched from the front gates
OL,15,Fof the Stormont estate in Belfast to
OL,16,Fthe steps of Parliament Buildings for
OL,17,Fthe lunchtime demonstration.
OL,19,FSeveral MLAs emerged from the building
OL,20,Fto join the event.
