OL,3,CDoctors warns of exodus over pay
OL,5,FChairwoman of the BMA's Northern
OL,6,FIreland junior doctor committee, Dr
OL,7,FFiona Griffin, told the colourful and
OL,8,Fnoisy rally that colleagues were
OL,9,Fleaving the region at an alarming rate.
OL,11,F"Over the past 15 years, we've seen
OL,12,Four pay eroded by over 30%.
OL,14,F"Inflation has soared, but our pay has
OL,15,Fnot kept up," she said.
