OL,3,CDoctors warns of exodus over pay
OL,5,F"The refusal to give appropriate and
OL,6,Ftimely pay awards has not only
OL,7,Fundervalued our hard work and
OL,8,Fdedication, but it has made it more
OL,9,Fdifficult to support families, more
OL,10,Fdifficult to pay the high costs
OL,11,Fassociated with our training and more
OL,12,Fdifficult to stay in the country.
OL,14,F"Many of our colleagues have made the
OL,15,Fdecision to leave this country in
OL,16,Fsearch of better opportunities
OL,17,Felsewhere.
OL,26,@mD@AOUvD@AOU
