OL,3,CDoctors warns of exodus over pay
OL,5,F"This is not a decision that they have
OL,6,Ftaken lightly, but rather a reflection
OL,7,Fof the dire situation that we all
OL,8,Fface."
OL,10,FDr Griffin disputed any suggestion the
OL,11,FBMA was exaggerating its warnings
OL,12,Faround the number of doctors
OL,13,Femigrating.
OL,15,F"We know who's leaving because it's us
OL,16,Fpicking up the shifts that are left
OL,17,Fbehind and we're having the added
OL,18,Fpleasure of seeing them out there on
OL,19,Fsandy beaches in Australia on their
OL,20,FInstagram," she said.
