OL,3,CDoctors warns of exodus over pay
OL,5,F"Our NHS is losing talented and
OL,6,Fdedicated professionals every day.
OL,8,F"And this exodus is a direct result of
OL,9,Fthe Department of Health's failure to
OL,10,Fadequately support and compensate us."
OL,12,FDr Griffin continued: "We're not
OL,13,Fasking for special treatment.
OL,15,F"We're asking for what is fair and
OL,16,Fjust, we're asking for recognition of
OL,17,Four hard work, our dedication and our
OL,18,Fcontribution to the health and well
OL,19,Fbeing of society.
OL,26,@mD@AOUpD@AOUrD@fO]tD@WOUwD@AOU
