OL,3,CDoctors warns of exodus over pay
OL,5,F"We're asking for a pay structure that
OL,6,Freflects the true value of our work,
OL,7,Fthat allows us to live without
OL,8,Ffinancial anxiety, and enables us to
OL,9,Fcontinue to provide the best possible
OL,10,Fcare for our patients."
OL,12,FShe added: "For too long have
OL,13,Fhealthcare staff been at the bottom of
OL,14,Fthe list of priorities and right now
OL,15,Fwe say enough is enough."
OL,17,FIn a statement, the Department of
OL,18,FHealth said it expected widespread
OL,19,Fdisruption to services across Thursday
OL,20,Fand Friday as a result of the strike.
