OL,5,FIt said that when the ballot for the
OL,6,Findustrial action was launched, junior
OL,7,Fdoctors, along with all health service
OL,8,Fstaff, had not received a pay award
OL,9,Ffor 2023/24.
OL,11,FThe department said that was no longer
OL,12,Fthe case and a backdated 2023/24 pay
OL,13,Faward for junior doctors will be paid
OL,14,Fthis month, with its terms in line
OL,15,Fwith the recommendations of the
OL,16,Fnational pay review body.
